<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">旧唐书</span>列传</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">卷五十一 列传第一 后妃上：高祖<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%86%E7%9A%87%E5%90%8E">太穆皇后</a>窦氏、太宗<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%87%E5%BE%B7%E7%9A%87%E5%90%8E/10955864" data-lemmaid="10955864">文德皇后</a>长孙氏、贤妃徐氏、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%97%E5%BA%9F%E5%90%8E%E7%8E%8B%E6%B0%8F">高宗废后王氏</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%89%AF%E5%A8%A3">良娣</a>萧氏、中宗<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%92%8C%E6%80%9D%E7%9A%87%E5%90%8E">和思皇后</a>赵氏、中宗<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%9F%A6%E5%BA%B6%E4%BA%BA">韦庶人</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%98%E6%98%AD%E5%AE%B9">上官昭容</a>、睿宗<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%82%83%E6%98%8E%E7%9A%87%E5%90%8E">肃明皇后</a>刘氏、睿宗<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%98%AD%E6%88%90%E7%9A%87%E5%90%8E">昭成皇后</a>窦氏、玄宗废后王氏、玄宗<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%B4%9E%E9%A1%BA%E7%9A%87%E5%90%8E">贞顺皇后</a>武氏、玄宗<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%A8%E8%B4%B5%E5%A6%83/32218" data-lemmaid="32218">杨贵妃</a><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:146px; float: right;">
